  "text": "In addition, the physicochemical features determine drug loading, drug release, and nanoparticle stability [CITATION_1] . For the evaluation of the three types of fucoidan/chitosan nanoparticles' ability as an oral delivery system, quercetin was incorporated. Table 2 presents the physicochemical characterization of blank and quercetin (Q)-loaded fucoidan/chitosan nanoparticles, for the three ratios under study.",
